  <brief_title>Transversus Abdominis Plane Block and Postoperative Pain After Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Subcostal Transversus Abdominis Plane Block on Early Postoperative Pain in Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy: Randomized, Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
